_sText:
This is a mod of the original Cathedral map with improved gameplay
and alterations for better FPS.
It includes multiple new features, such as:
> Better catacomb access (check out the graveyard)
> Air Vents
> Improved CT cover on balcony
> Removed tower door locking mechanism
> CT access to top floor of tower
> More cover for CTs on the ground
> Expanded rooms for better interaction
> The Rat-room is open
> Improved roof access
> Improved BOT navigation
